3. Medical and Dental appointments shall be filled out properly, especially dates of appointment and signatures;
4. Ensure that medical (and dental) appointments are timely scheduled and properly documented.
Kazah Services, LLC through the  LCCA/Administrator, shall oversee that these requirements are followed and accomplished.
"
